        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does Bizee.com cost to form an LLC?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bizee’s service fee starts with their Basic package, but you also pay your state’s mandatory filing fee, which varies. The Basic package often starts at $0 (plus state fee) and includes the first year of registered agent service. Their website clearly breaks down the total cost before you pay.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Bizee.com a legitimate company?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, absolutely. Bizee (formerly Incfile) has been in business for years and has successfully formed over 200,000 business entities. They are a legitimate online legal filing service with numerous positive reviews across multiple platforms.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is the difference between Bizee and a lawyer?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bizee is a filing service that efficiently and affordably handles the standard paperwork for forming an entity like an LLC. A lawyer provides personalized legal advice, custom operating agreements, and guidance for complex situations. For a standard formation, Bizee is a cost-effective solution. For complex multi-member agreements or specific legal questions, consulting an attorney is wise.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Do I need an EIN from Bizee, or can I get it myself?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can easily get an EIN for free directly from the IRS website. Bizee offers it as a convenient add-on service so you can have everything in one place and avoid the IRS process, but it is not mandatory to use their service.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
